## ORDERS ##

**15. Panzergrenadier-Division assets:**
* `15. PzG-Div HQ` relocate to nothern side of SINT-OEDENRODE, close to intersection with road leading to OLLAND.
* `15. PzG-Div Logistics` relocate to OLLAND
* `Panzer-Aufk-Bat 115` relocate to central forest, (grid 50, 31)
* `Pionier-Bat 33` relocate to SINT-OEDENRODE, setup explosive charges onto the bridge there, over DOMMEL river.
* `Flak-Bat 315` relocate to position around 1-1,5km east from SINT-OEDENRODE (grid 44, 32), use small forest for cover, provide AA defense

**Panzer-Artillerie-Regiment 33:**
* `I. Battalion/Panzer-Art-Reg 33` relocate to position around 1 km north of SINT-OEDENRODE, close to road towards VEGHEL (West side of the road)
* `II. Battalion/Panzer-Art-Reg 33` relocate to position around 1 km north of SINT-OEDENRODE, close to road towards SCHIJNDEL 

**Sturmgeschütz-Brigade 115:**
*` I. Bat/Stug-Brigade 115` Relocate to BOXTEL.
* `II. Bat/Stug-Brigade 115` Relocate to BOXTEL.
* `III. Bat/Stug-Brigade 115` conduct coordinated general assult towards BEST.

**Panzer-Grenadier-Regiment 104:**
* `I. Bat/PzG-Reg 104` carry on.
* `II. Bat/PzG-Reg 104` hold position, dig in.
* `III. Bat/PzG-Reg 104` carry on.

Panzer-Grenadier-Regiment 115:
* `I. Bat/PzG-Reg 115` attack BEST through forest, south of the current position, and go around enemy positions.
* `II. Bat/PzG-Reg 115` conduct coordinated general assult towards BEST.
* `III. Bat/PzG-Reg 115` conduct coordinated general assult towards BEST.

